        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"model\": \"llama3.1:8b-instruct-q6_K\",\n  \"prompt\": \"Analyze this email for anything not promotional.\\n\\nRULES:\\n1. First, list the 'signs of importance' (high-autority sender, urgent subject line, imminent deadline included, direct action required, personnally addressed, financial implications, legal relevance).\\n2. Then, assign a 'priority_score' (1-5).\\n3. Finally, set 'is_important' to true if score > 2\\n\\nEMAIL:\\n{{ $json.snippet }}\\n\\nOUTPUT FORMAT (JSON ONLY):\\n{\\n  \\\"reasoning\\\": \\\"...\\\",\\n  \\\"priority_score\\\": X,\\n  \\\"is_important\\\": boolean\\n}\",\n  \"stream\": false,\n  \"format\": \"json\"\n}\n",
